OL,3,CUK set for unusually warm week: How
OL,4,Chigh could temperatures get where you
OL,5,Clive?
OL,7,FHighs across central and southeastern
OL,8,FEngland could rise as high as 18C on
OL,9,FWednesday which would put us around 9-
OL,10,F10C above the seasonal average.
OL,12,FWith plenty of sunshine across much of
OL,13,FEngland and parts of Wales, it's a
OL,14,Fwell deserved break from the
OL,15,Finterminable cloud and rain so far
OL,16,Fthis winter.
OL,18,FCould these temperatures break any
OL,19,Frecords?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1771851970
OL,3,CUK set for unusually warm week: How
OL,4,Chigh could temperatures get where you
OL,5,Clive?
OL,7,FTemperatures into the high teens on
OL,8,FWednesday are still a little below the
OL,9,Fdaily record of 20.6C set back in
OL,10,F2019, and the February UK record of
OL,11,F21.2C also set in 2019.
OL,13,FHowever, it's possible that some local
OL,14,Frecords could be challenged, and it's
OL,15,Fhighly likely to be the warmest day of
OL,16,Fthe year so far.
OL,18,FWill it stay dry during this mild
OL,19,Fspell?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
