OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1771851970
OL,3,CUK set for unusually warm week: How
OL,4,Chigh could temperatures get where you
OL,5,Clive?
OL,7,FA northwest/southeast split is
OL,8,Fexpected to develop across the UK over
OL,9,Fthe next few days as the jet stream
OL,10,Fshifts a little further northwards
OL,11,Fdirecting the main focus of the rain
OL,12,Faway from the southwest to more
OL,13,Fnorthwesterly areas.
OL,15,FThis welcome respite for flood
OL,16,Faffected areas in the West Country for
OL,17,Fexample will allow some time for water
OL,18,Flevels to settle somewhat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
