PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1771851970
OL,3,CUK set for unusually warm week: How
OL,4,Chigh could temperatures get where you
OL,5,Clive?
OL,7,FOccasional showers cannot be ruled
OL,8,Fout, particularly early in the week or
OL,9,Fin eastern parts, whilst western and
OL,10,Fnorthwestern regions will experience
OL,11,Fthe heaviest and most frequent rain.
OL,13,FHow about the rest of the UK?
OL,15,FTemperatures should rise above average
OL,16,Ffor the whole of the UK this week - in
OL,17,Fpart thanks to a much less cold
OL,18,Fsouthwesterly airflow bringing in
OL,19,Fwarmer air - but it will certainly be
OL,20,Fwarmest across the southeast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
