OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1771851970
OL,3,CUK set for unusually warm week: How
OL,4,Chigh could temperatures get where you
OL,5,Clive?
OL,7,FHow long will these warmer
OL,8,Ftemperatures last?
OL,10,FFor most of this week before dipping
OL,11,Fback down to around the seasonal
OL,12,Faverage by the weekend.
OL,14,FThe overall picture for this week
OL,16,FSouth West: Mostly dry, sunny spells
OL,17,Fand temperatures in the high teens.
OL,19,FNorth and West: Cloudy, frequent rain
OL,20,Fand temperatures in the range of 12-
OL,21,F14C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
